### Get published events sorted by start date
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=status eq 'Published'&$orderby=startDate
 
### Get events filtered by type Workshop
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=eventType eq 'Workshop'
 
### Get all registrations for AI Summit event
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Registrations?$filter=event_ID eq aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa
 
### Post a new registration
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Registrations
Content-Type: application/json
 
{
  "ID": "bbbb1111-2222-3333-4444-555555555555",
  "event_ID": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
  "attendeeName": "Vicky Kaushal",
  "attendeeEmail": "vicky@example.com",
  "attendeePhone": "9876543210",
  "company": "Wipro",
  "ticketType": "VIP",
  "registrationDate": "2025-07-15",
  "status": "Confirmed",
  "amountPaid": 2000,
  "paymentId": "PAY999"
}
 
### Get speakers sorted by rating descending
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Speakers?$orderby=rating desc
 
### Get events with available seats
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=registeredCount lt maxAttendees
 
### Update event status from Draft to Published
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events(bbbbbbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbbbbbbbbbb)
Content-Type: application/json
 
{
  "status": "Published"
}
 
### Post feedback for an event
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Feedback
Content-Type: application/json
 
{
  "ID": "99999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999999",
  "event_ID": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
  "attendeeEmail": "vicky@example.com",
  "overallRating": 5,
  "contentRating": 5,
  "venueRating": 4,
  "speakerRating": 5,
  "comment": "Excellent event",
  "submittedAt": "2025-08-12T10:00:00Z"
}
 